    <div class="container-narrow">
      <h2 class="text-center">What Participants Are Saying</h2>
      <div class="testimonials-grid">
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <div class="quote-icon">"</div>
          <p class="testimonial-text">The Wim Hof Method with Dr. Maks has been transformative. The combination of breathing exercises and cold exposure has helped me manage stress better than anything I've tried before. The community support makes all the difference.</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <strong>Michael T.</strong>
            <span class="star-rating">‚òÖ‚òÖ‚òÖ‚òÖ‚òÖ</span>
