        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <div class="quote-icon">"</div>
          <p class="testimonial-text">I was skeptical about ice baths at first, but Dr. Maks's guidance made it accessible and safe. After just a few sessions, I noticed improved energy levels and mental clarity. This practice has become an essential part of my wellness routine.</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <strong>Sarah L.</strong>
            <span class="star-rating">‚òÖ‚òÖ‚òÖ‚òÖ‚òÖ</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <div class="quote-icon">"</div>
          <p class="testimonial-text">The Wim Hof workshops at Physica Medica are incredible. Dr. Maks combines his physical therapy expertise with the method perfectly. I've seen improvements in my athletic recovery and overall resilience to stress.</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <strong>James R.</strong>
            <span class="star-rating">‚òÖ‚òÖ‚òÖ‚òÖ‚òÖ</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="wim-hof-content section-spacing">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <h2>Wim Hof Method Workshops & Training</h2>
      <p>Dr. Maks offers both group workshops and one-on-one Wim Hof Method instruction. Learn proper breathing techniques, safe cold exposure practices, and mental strategies in a supportive environment.</p>

      <div class="cta-box">
        <h3>Experience the Wim Hof Method</h3>
        <p>Contact us to learn about upcoming workshops or schedule a private session.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="cta-button">Get Started</a>
